---
title: White Sesame Teriyaki Beef with Bok Choy and Jasmine Rice
description: All the flavor and convenience of this takeout favorite without the fat sounds like a win-win to us. In this stir-fry, beef tips are marinated in a sweet glaze, tossed with colorful greens, and served over a bed of jasmine rice.
